oracle.title: Oracle AI
oracle.description:
Oracle AI is an artificial intelligence that is capable of long term memory, tool usage, and more!
Oracle has been trained on datasets such as community submissions, wikipedia articles, and other sources, giving it the unique ability to learn and comment about fictional stories and events as soon as they happen!

bluemapwrapper.title: BlueMapWrapper
bluemapwrapper.description: BlueMapWrapper is a Python library that lets you easily interact with BlueMap Data, allowing you to easily parse markers, player locations, plugin data, and more!

ratmod.title: Rat Mod
ratmod.description: Rat mod is a Minecraft Fabric mod that adds rats, cheese, and more into your game!
